      "type": "ApplicabilityConstraint",
      "name": "Applicability constraint: non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw under ASTM F1717 static loading",
      "description": "Model applicability is constrained to non-cannulated pedicle screw constructs of 7.5 mm nominal diameter assessed under ASTM F1717 quasi-static compression-bending protocol. Results are not applicable to cannulated designs, dynamic fatigue loading, or screw diameters outside the 6.5–8.5 mm range validated herein."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
