      "type": "OperatingEnvelope",
      "name": "Operating envelope: ASTM F1717 static compression-bending conditions",
      "description": "Displacement-controlled quasi-static loading at 25 mm/min crosshead speed; applied load range 0–3500 N; construct offset 40 mm per ASTM F1717; ambient temperature 23 ± 2 °C; screw diameter 7.5 mm ± 0.05 mm; titanium alloy Ti-6Al-4V ELI material; UHMWPE block fixtures per standard."
    }
